        "Description": "- Start at bazaar entrance\r- Get screwdriver at electronics street\r- Get fortune teller disguise and kill him with propane tank\r- Go to target &quot;Nabhan&quot;, expose wire and turn on power\r- Go to target &quot;Dabir&quot;, use emetic syringe and drown him\r- Go to target &quot;Terry&quot; and puncture oil drum\r- Go to target &quot;Ellinor&quot; and push her\r- Exit level",
